# Pre-commit gate.
#
# Runs lint-staged: oxlint + biome format-check on changed files only,
# typically finishing in <500ms. Mirrors the CI lint job (lint, format,
# deadcode, dupes) so failures are caught locally before push.
#
# Skip with `git commit --no-verify` in an emergency; the CI job is the
# authoritative gate.

bunx lint-staged
